        <item>
            <title>【評測】Mac mini M4 2024：進階用家最應該買的 Apple 電腦，效能、日常應用詳細評測分析</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/07/mac-mini-2024-review/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mac-mini-2024-review</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/07/mac-mini-2024-review/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 13:03:42 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流動電腦]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[評測]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[mac]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mac mini]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mac mini 2024]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mac mini M4]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1273818</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 一口氣推出全新 M4 系列的 MacBook Pro、Mac mini 和 iMac，當中 Mac mini 以全新輕巧外型吸引全球 Apple 用家注意。實際上它內置的 M4 / M4 Pro 處理器，將這個只有手掌大小的盒子，成為可替代以往坐枱式電腦，就同有了 Mini PC 大家不去黃金砌機一樣，成為電腦上的一個革命（起碼在 Apple 電腦來説）。這款小型電腦在硬件上有顯著提升，運行日常設計、影片剪輯軟件都非常夠做，更支援 Apple Intelligence 提升工作效率，是追求效能，但不是追求終極效能的用家之中，性價比超強的選擇。以下將詳細評測 Mac mini，為你説明為何「進階用家」應用要買的是 Mac mini 而不是其他 Apple 電腦。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03644-scaled.jpg"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273832" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03644-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03644-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03644-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03649-scaled.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273834" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03649-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03649-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03649-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>相關影片</h2><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_57075"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/G9wF-ei92Ao?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><h2>進一步精簡的外型設計</h2><p>Mac mini 已成為了一部「高性價比版本的 Mac Studio」。</p><p>早前外國已有跑分，證明 M4 Pro 版 Mac mini 的 CPU 跑分能夠勝過 M2 Ultra 的 Mac Studio 達到 25%。這就反映瞭如果你對電腦效能的需要，只是圖像處理、影片／聲音剪輯、創作等用途，而非大型電影製作，考慮到價錢，Mac mini 是一個性價比極高的選擇。當然 Mac Studio 有它的好處，這些我們都知道，但考慮到當時 M2 Ultra 版的 Mac Studio 售價是 HK$32,999，而今次新機就算是 M4 Pro 版售價都只是 HK$10,599，很粗暴的比較之下，大家發現如果可以犧性某些 Mac Studio 的特點，Mac mini 變成了很多進階用家直接的選擇。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110720h21-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273856" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110720h21-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110720h21-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110720h21-2.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03664-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273835" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03664-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03664-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03664-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110792516-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273885 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110792516-694x387.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="387" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110792516-694x387.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110792516-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>特別是對於小編來説，平時需要剪片、上網看網頁、處理圖片，以往 M2 年代也是覺得很夠用。像我這類接受不到平價電腦，但又不至於要求一部怪獸級電腦的人來説，Mac mini 就非常吸引。像小編這類用家，好多以前都用 iMac 27 吋。不過自從 Apple 不再出 iMac 27 吋之後，大家就將目光轉移到 Mac mini。今時今日 Mac mini 在 Apple 電腦中的角色，已經同以前大大不同。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110720h21-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273857" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110720h21-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110720h21-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110720h21-3.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲重量只有約 650g 的 Mac mini，可以帶去旅行駁酒店電視，當電腦用或睇片</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03663-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273886" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03663-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03663-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03663-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲實際長闊度只有一隻精妙滑鼠多一點</p><p>新一代的 Mac mini 體積縮小了超過一半，由上代的 7.75&#215;7.75 吋壓縮至僅 5&#215;5 吋，從以往的扁平造型轉變成更立體的方磚設計，類似於縮小版的 Mac Studio，重量只有約 650 克。這種輕巧設計無疑更適合需要節省空間的用家，你甚至可以 mount 在電腦熒幕之後。它也容易擺放入你的旅行袋，出門去旅行駁到酒店的電視，用其簡單工作或睇片，都是非常方便。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire0010.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273858" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire0010-694x509.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="509" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire0010-694x509.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire0010.jpg 1227w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire001211536x864.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273859" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire001211536x864-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire001211536x864-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire001211536x864.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲這是上次我們借用的 Mac mini 2023 版本，可見要放下它還是不易。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03644-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273860" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03644-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03644-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03644-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今次 Mac mini 2024 版本，一體感更好，你會發現桌面多了好多空間。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03640.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273861" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03640-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03640-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03640.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03650-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273882" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03650-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03650-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03650-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
